dct_description_sm: Oriented with north toward upper left of sheet.
Latitudinal and longitudinal lines along margins.
Decorative cartouches, compass rose, shields, fauna.
Shows White Sea, Mourmanskoy Sea, Black Sea, Caspian Sea.
Pictorial vignette with figures: The habit of Russians.
Inset map (bird's eye view of city, with index): The famous and imperiall city of Moscow.
5 ancillary maps (views): Russche Narva; Archangel; The Emperours court; A hott house; A mill of Russia.
